section elementor-element elementor-element-422adf4 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default pxl-section-static-pos-no pxl-section-overflow-hidden-no\" data-id=\"422adf4\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\n                \n                <div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no \">\n                <div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-a6d0311 pxl-column-element-default pxl-column-fullwidth-no\" data-id=\"a6d0311\" data-element_type=\"column\">\r\n        <div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\r\n                    \t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-99abc65 pxl-heading-layout-1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-pxl_heading\" data-id=\"99abc65\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"pxl_heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"pxl-heading-wrap d-flex layout1\">\n    <div class=\"pxl-heading-inner\">\n                <h4 class=\"heading-title\">\n                        What determines the color of coffee after brewing?                    <\/h4>\n            <\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d57a41 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-pxl_text_editor\" data-id=\"0d57a41\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"pxl_text_editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<div id=\"pxl_text_editor-0d57a41-1846\" class=\"pxl-text-editor-wrap d-flex\" >\n    <div class=\"pxl-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n        <p>Quantitatively, the color of coffee beans after roasting can be measured using the Agtron Gourmet or Commercial Scale. But usually, these quantitative measurements are quite expensive and not really common.<\/p><p>So it will be supplemented or replaced with more relative roast color determinations, such as \u201clight\u201d, \u201cmedium\u201d or \u201cdark\u201d. On the consumer side, color is often the first measure of consumer-created quality, making it a basic indicator of sensory quality. In addition, product-specific color changes.<\/p>    <\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t                    <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        \t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t                    <\/div>\r\n        <\/div>\r\n        \t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Holistically pontificate installed base portals after maintainable products. Phosfluorescently engage worldwide methodologies.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4398,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"templates\/pxl-single-template-2.php","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[54,55],"class_list":["post-4419","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uncategorized","tag-burger","tag-fast-food"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4419","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4419"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4419\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4420,"href":"https:\/\/demo.7iquid.com\/basilico\/fastfood\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4419\/revisions\/4420"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https